Renders subobject sections for a category. For each subobject type
declared on the category (or any ancestor, via Category/collect-ancestors),
emits a heading and an #ask that renders each instance through
Category/subobject-instance (which itself reuses Category/table).

Subobject types are discovered from Subobject field declarations on the
ancestor chain: {{#ask: [[-Has subobject::<ancestors>]] [[Category:Subobject field]] | ?For category}}.

Parameters:
* category - The category name whose subobject types should be rendered
* page - The parent page whose subobject instances should be listed;
         defaults to {{FULLPAGENAME}}.
